{"tid":551273,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾日見到老母","createTime":"2018-02-05T13:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T16:31:21.000Z","uid":65448,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"697d097ebdaa59cc642c846a8d5d527f1f83f6f5","tid":551273,"uid":65448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"行路吉下吉下，<br />\n原來佢腳痛到行每一步都好辛苦，<br />\n佢星期六仲特登落去買早餐比我呢個廢青食，<br />\n星期六我仲發佢脾氣，而我居然無擦覺。<br />\n到今日原來佢返唔到工，<br />\n自己一個人去睇醫生，打止痛針，話唔想留醫院。<br />\n痛到吉下吉下，<br />\n仲買餸、煮飯比我呢個不孝子食，仲做哂所有家務。<br />\n返到屋企，我個心真係那住那住痛。<br />\n媽媽，對不起，我一直都唔識珍惜你對我的好，今日起我唔會再要你咁辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n(現實唔敢同人share, 借個窿比我埋下呢件心事)"},{"pid":"12977c3dd79068a523e6ed7c36caf71c6100a4f9","tid":551273,"uid":38543,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:15:37.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"2c55159617123ae476c501dbd25ad1b25a5428da","tid":551273,"uid":132847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:18:09.000Z","msg":"見到原來呢兩隻字已經想屌鳩你<br />\n原乜撚嘢來 平時唔識關心下老豆老母？<br />\n生舊叉燒好過生你"},{"pid":"49d2035dbaae86499ebe8c090299ea3fdeec9a0e","tid":551273,"uid":828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:18:29.000Z","msg":"我都好想知你跟住會做d咩黎令你老母無咁辛苦"},{"pid":"f7856e120b0fa9c0d54534a6ad2729dff510ea3e","tid":551273,"uid":7615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"你Forward 自己個post比老母睇啦"},{"pid":"aa09e4800899719221961a473fc3a6d2a14063fe","tid":551273,"uid":121257,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"當連登仔係你老母？ 呢啲野親口同你老母講啦"},{"pid":"829b1784f061845f75bd463c22e4fe39f7b3b5c3","tid":551273,"uid":33631,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"同老母道歉啦 上連登開post做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f04fc1d6e88c6ceb0fbc053f4d3af4b3748ca8","tid":551273,"uid":57659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T1